===Noun===
#A '''rhythmic unit''' is a [[durational pattern]] which occupies a period of time equivalent to a [[pulse]] or pulses on an underlying [[metric level]]. It may be [[metric]], [[intrametric]], [[contrametric]], or [[extrametric]].
:(DeLone et. al. (Eds.), 1975, chap. 3)

See: [[rhythm]]

